DISCIPLINARY CASES

2010-1217. Erie-Huron Grievance Commt. v. Stoll.

This cause is pending before the court upon the filing of a report by the Board of Commissioners on Grievances and Discipline. On July 23, 2010, the board filed a motion to supplement the record. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered by this court that the motion is granted.
